{
  "stem": "3341.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after having-- with almost-- I finished four years of the high school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I suddenly changed my view what I want to be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, a-- a child of-- of a Jewish family, a prosperous Jewish family, they always wanted even that time to study for a lawyer or a doctor and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- this didn't change.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't like-- when it came to the third year of the high school, we started to learn Latin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Latin was a very difficult language, and I didn't like it very much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So naturally, I wasn't keen to learn something which I didn't like.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there-- it was a quite a hard study.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was under the influence of two very good friends of mine in the same class, and those two youngsters were very gifted comics.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like all school children, they developed such liking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those two friends of mine, they said, oh, they didn't like Latin right away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, we will-- next year, we are going to enroll in the dramatic art academy to be a actor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it appealed to me [LAUGHS] was probably because I didn't say anything at home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Secretly, I enrolled also in the dramatic art.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was halfway of your eight-year study of [NON-ENGLISH]-- it was eight years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When my parents found out, then-- what he wants to be a actor?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were terribly annoyed because who wants-- actor was not a very respectable profession.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was more or less considered like a gypsy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And gypsies and actors were not the favorite of the people anywhere in Europe at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
